               <head>Bahjat al-mabāhij by Ḥasan ibn Ḥusayn Shīʻī Sabzavārī</head>
               <msContents class="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh2008104277">
                  <summary>A Shi'ite work on the life, merits and miracles of the Prophet and the Imams, abridged from the 
            <title>Mabāhij al-muhaj</title> by 
            <persName>Quṭb al-Dīn al-Kaydarī</persName>
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_578A-item1">
                     <author key="viaf_4578593">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Shīʿī Sabzavārī, Ḥasan ibn Ḥusayn, 14th cent.</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">شيعى سبزوارى، ملا حسن بن حسين</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_11007">Bahjat al-Mabāhij</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_11007">بهجة المباهج</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>The work is preceded by three folios (ff. iii-v) which deal with events preceding the Prophet's birth</p>
                     </note>
                     <note>
                        <p>The original manuscript (ff. iii-v, 21-347), in a good, clear nastaʻliq, within a red text frame, probably dates from the 17th century. Folios i-ii, 1-20 and 348-54 have been added
                later.</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
